WEBVTT

1
00:44:15.900 --> 00:44:17.910 
很有地位
It was a position of respect.

2
00:44:17.920 --> 00:44:20.660 
-不就是盯住雇员  -不让他们偷鸡摸狗
- Watch over the employees. - Make sure nobody steals.

3
00:44:20.670 --> 00:44:22.780 
还有很多别的职责
There were many responsibilities.

4
00:44:22.790 --> 00:44:25.250 
不管什么职责  都是忠诚为先
And they all depended on loyalty, didn't they?

5
00:44:25.260 --> 00:44:27.410 
忠诚  诚实
Loyalty and honesty.

6
00:44:27.420 --> 00:44:30.260 
-这两点你引以为豪  -我是努力争取
- You pride yourself on that. - I strive.

7
00:44:30.270 --> 00:44:33.040 
努力争取  努力争取
You strive. You strive.

8
00:44:33.930 --> 00:44:35.580 
你告诉过妻子吗
Did you even tell your wife?

9
00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:38.020 
-儿子们呢  -还是只带着钱跑了
- Your sons? - Or just leave with the money?

10
00:44:38.030 --> 00:44:39.790 
钱和情妇
The money and mistress.

11
00:44:40.160 --> 00:44:42.630 
她是卖内衣的
She worked behind the lingerie counter.

12
00:44:42.640 --> 00:44:44.390 
卖了多久
How long did that last?

13
00:44:45.960 --> 00:44:47.150 
没多久
Not long.

14
00:44:47.560 --> 00:44:49.670 
快乐总是不长久啊
So much for happiness, huh, Ed?

